tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE biometric_data (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    fingerprint_data BYTEA NOT NULL,
    retina_data BYTEA NOT NULL,
    face_data BYTEA NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE AccessLogs (
    log_id SERIAL,
    user_id INT,
    accessed_at TIMESTAMP,
    action VARCHAR(50),
    result VARCHAR(20)
);
